{
  "stem": "9728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you couldn't grab it, you did not eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they send us to the other place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They send up to the place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The place was-- also, during the way, on the way we were informed that we are going to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, we heard about Dachau, and we knew about Dachau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, as I said, it couldn't be worse than Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So just away from here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They sent us to Dachau, not to the headquarters in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Dachau is a city about 16 kilometers, about 11 miles from Munich.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "However, they send us to Kaufering.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Kaufering was under the supervision of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Dachau had the say about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they built around camps there which were-- Dachau was a camp that had held slaves staying there whatever the time was-- Jews or German or Poles or whatever-- to stay there, and-- and to kill them or-- or whatever to do.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "However, we were sent to a slave labor camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Before they're going to kill us, they wanted us to work, to work off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So this was the so-called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a-- It was a outside commander from-- from Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was Kaufering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Kaufering is a small village near the city of Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was probably about several miles from Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Landsberg is the famous city where Adolf Hitler, before he came to power, was in jail in Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there we had to work over there when we came to-- I'll come to that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They send us to Kaufering.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kaufering, again, was just a-- they built up the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They build up the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were there probably for about several weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we helped build up the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, the camp was more or less huts.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
